{"tid":972433,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Google擬向中國收Android授權費　華為、中興、小米及其他","createTime":"2019-01-07T11:28:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-08T02:46:55.000Z","uid":47714,"like":178,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"57d8abfce4d49777c9a1fb9dad893d8824178a2c","tid":972433,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T11:28:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/124/212127/1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eprice.com.hk%2Fmobile%2Ftalk%2F124%2F212127%2F1%2F&d=E%2F%2B5pn%2FqAz4%2Bd1X9LuAQFwdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=2c176d33\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/124/212127/1/</a><br />\n<br />\n日前 Android 的官方 Twitter 帳號透露，Google 將會在今年第三季向中國生產商收取授權費，華為、中興、小米等廠商都會受到影響。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/3c/page/2019/01/02/190102-35502-2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2F3c%2Fpage%2F2019%2F01%2F02%2F190102-35502-2.png&h=ebf9debe&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fc81c8b96ba0e3948dbe108df90173adba9e5f27","tid":972433,"uid":61545,"like":128,"dislike":1,"score":127,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T11:29:54.000Z","msg":"一早應該要<br />\n成日咁囂張偷人技術然後當自家研發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"828645ee50284e74f0dc9721b46aba378eb8c1c2","tid":972433,"uid":22675,"like":9,"dislike":38,"score":-29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T11:31:56.000Z","msg":"已經証實咗係流料"},{"pid":"d197bcf69ad58a2a15a4f48dad22912fa016722f","tid":972433,"uid":134323,"like":67,"dislike":0,"score":67,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T11:33:24.000Z","msg":"唔應該收<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n應該直接唔俾佢地用"},{"pid":"3fdb877fb048d352ceb38452e59fe2e555a4fa97","tid":972433,"uid":10757,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T11:34:26.000Z","msg":"爆料網站 Slashleaks 日前上傳一張宣稱來自 Android Twitter 帳號的截圖，截圖內的貼文寫著，「我們準備於 2019 年第三季向中國生產商收取費用，當中包括華為、中興、小米和其他智慧手機生產商。」Slashleaks 表示，該貼文在發出不久後就被 Google 刪除。<br />\n<br />\n一直以來 Android 系統都是免費和開源的，因為預載在系統的 Google 搜尋和 Chrome 瀏覽器帶來收入，Google 沒有向使用 Android 的廠商收取授權費用。不過去年 7 月歐洲議會指 Google 濫用 Android 的支配地位，逼使廠商預載搜尋和 Chrome，並罰款 50 億美元後，Google 要配合歐洲議會的要求，讓廠商選擇是否預載上述兩個軟體，並且因應裝置尺寸和所屬國家，支付每部裝置 2.5 至 40 美元的授權費。<br />\n<br />\n有分析指 Google 因為上述改變，所以打算向中國手機品牌收取費用。網站 BGR 就事件向 Google 查詢，結果卻峰迴路轉，Google 否認曾經發過有關貼文，更向 BGR 確認該貼文並非真實。"},{"pid":"48811d8a72ac922f3c733d7510f6f6a5dcd57fdc","tid":972433,"uid":22675,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T11:34:34.000Z","msg":"（3/1 晚上更新：Google 回應網站 BGR 的查詢，否認有發出該 Tweet，並表示確認該 Tweet 並非真實。）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/124/212127/1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eprice.com.hk%2Fmobile%2Ftalk%2F124%2F212127%2F1%2F&d=E%2F%2B5pn%2FqAz4%2Bd1X9LuAQFwdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=2c176d33\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/124/212127/1/</a>"},{"pid":"fc147ab09e4ecb2e5a4c4c8a32cd9df2d6af4299","tid":972433,"uid":22675,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"fc81c8b96ba0e3948dbe108df90173adba9e5f27","tid":972433,"uid":61545,"like":128,"dislike":1,"score":127,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T11:29:54.000Z","msg":"一早應該要<br />\n成日咁囂張偷人技術然後當自家研發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T11:35:38.000Z","msg":"（3/1 晚上更新：Google 回應網站 BGR 的查詢，否認有發出該 Tweet，並表示確認該 Tweet 並非真實。）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/124/212127/1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eprice.com.hk%2Fmobile%2Ftalk%2F124%2F212127%2F1%2F&d=E%2F%2B5pn%2FqAz4%2Bd1X9LuAQFwdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=2c176d33\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/124/212127/1/</a><br />\n已經証實咗係流料"},{"pid":"d1b26300e0d0a065176232648936b4b03b4667db","tid":972433,"uid":22554,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T11:35:57.000Z","msg":"一早要收, 大陸D 電話好似BAN 左GOOGLE PLAY, 你又唔俾人係STORE 買野, 又唔使俾授權費, 真係當人義工咩"},{"pid":"4bc88d0b3120948d401c40ad3c2bbecb5aaebb01","tid":972433,"uid":150609,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T11:36:33.000Z","msg":"厲害了的國咁勁 仲唔自己寫個os<br />\n<br />\n用埋d美帝window android<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b7dce55df8132e693b35ba2cf803d935353a156","tid":972433,"uid":63846,"like":3,"dislike":34,"score":-31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T11:37:57.000Z","msg":"Open source 都叫偷技術，child登仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"492ab192436b91708c3ba94698e994f7be122a6f","tid":972433,"uid":5159,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T11:40:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddd445b32b5be794556bc16167ac11ecd1b75567","tid":972433,"uid":47714,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T11:41:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20190106001684-260412\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinatimes.com%2Frealtimenews%2F20190106001684-260412&d=E%2F%2B5pn%2FqAz4%2Bd1X9LuAQFwdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=e556f831\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20190106001684-260412</a><br />\n<br />\nGoogle 沒有跳出來否認這條烏龍新聞的內容，雅虎中國總裁、現任奇虎360公司董事長的周鴻禕認為內容在未來很有可能會成真。"},{"pid":"bd0977fc3dcd04401a70bdf0ca01acbadc1297c3","tid":972433,"uid":134323,"like":38,"dislike":1,"score":37,"quote":{"pid":"8b7dce55df8132e693b35ba2cf803d935353a156","tid":972433,"uid":63846,"like":3,"dislike":34,"score":-31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T11:37:57.000Z","msg":"Open source 都叫偷技術，child登仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T12:26:37.000Z","msg":"Open source 唔代表放棄全部權益<br />\n<br />\n你分下咩叫 mit bsd Apache license 先出黎柒好無？"},{"pid":"328eea2513c6f76395bfde6136c1f30281c71688","tid":972433,"uid":51720,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"